    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2026-03-20</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2026-03-23T13:50:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution recognizes the importance of fully funding the Department of Homeland Security (DHS).</p><p>The resolution also (1) cautions that Americans are at greater risk each day&nbsp;DHS is subject to a lapse in appropriations, and (2) expresses gratitude to DHS employees for their commitment to protect the United States.&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
